 FACEBOOK\nBUY TICKETS ON EVENTBRITE\nEVENTS\n🌮🍹 Taco & Tequila Tuesday\nLove tequila? We do too 😃 Every Tuesday, come in for a tequila flight! For $20, you get three 1 oz. pours of three of our tequilas. And at our Beltline location, our delicious tacos are just $3 from Noon to 6 PM on Tuesdays! AND at our West Midtown location, our fresh guacamole and queso are just $7 from 5 PM to close!\n🥑 Guacamole and Margarita Making Class\nBook a guacamole and margarita making class for you and your friends or as a work happy hour! Check out this testimonial from the first one we ever did!\nâAs the first group to book a guacamole and margarita tasting, it was an absolute pleasure. The staff was incredibly attentive and catered to our every need to accommodate our group of twelve for a team event. Each of us were given individually packaged and pre-measured ingredients for a clean and safe experience. The instructors were fantastic, and the guacamole was even better than I imagined! I even got a second one to bring home. The margaritas were so delicious and the Guac y Margys team was kind enough to give us all our own personal cocktail shakers to make our margaritas at home. I would book this event a million times over. Best guacamole and margarita making experience ever!â - Sydney\n🦌 Vixen's Christmas Bar\nDuring the month of December, Guac y Margys turns into Vixen's Christmas Bar, complete with our Twelve Drinks of Christmas menu! 🎅\n💌 Keep up to date with all things GyM\nSign up for our email newsletter. Don't worry, we won't blow up your inbox. We only send 2 or 3 per month.\nSIGN UP FOR OUR MAIL LIST",
